	<source xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xml:lang="en">“Inclusive Language Guide,” Cal State East Bay, n.d., accessed December 3, 2024, https://www.csueastbay.edu/universitycommunications/inclusive-language-guide.html</source>
	<title xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xml:lang="en">Savage</title>
