<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/s_31">
	<rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#SuggestionNote"/>
	<modified xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-11-08</modified>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">Do not use the term retarded or other iterations. If you are going to use it in a quote, consider that decision carefully, as the word is particularly charged. Instead, always try to specify the type of disability being referenced. Otherwise, the term 'intellectually disabled' is acceptable. Consider using people-first language, as in 'a person with an intellectual disability' rather than 'an intellectually disabled person.' If known, use the term the described person prefers.</rdf:value>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_188_en"/>
</rdf:Description>

<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/s_43">
	<rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#SuggestionNote"/>
	<modified xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-11-11</modified>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">Try to be specific about the disability of the affected person.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="it">Cercando di essere specifico su che disabilità.</rdf:value>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_33_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_34_it"/>
</rdf:Description>

<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/s_23">
	<rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#SuggestionNote"/>
	<modified xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-12-20</modified>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="nl">Deze term kan worden gebruikt als het gaat om een bijvoeglijk naamwoord; het gebruik als zelfstandig naamwoord dat verwijst naar mensen wordt afgeraden.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="de">Dieser Begriff kann als Adjektiv verwendet werden. Von seiner Verwendung als Substantiv, um Personen zu bezeichnen, wird abgeraten.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="it">Assolutamente da evitare l'uso come sostantivi, solo come aggettivi.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="fr">Ce terme peut être utilisé pour désigner un adjectif ; son utilisation en tant que substantif désignant des personnes est déconseillée.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">This term can be used as an adjective; its use as a noun referring to people is discouraged.</rdf:value>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_21_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_23_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_24_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_27_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_25_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_39_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_82_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_79_it"/>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_81_it"/>
</rdf:Description>

<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/s_21">
	<rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#SuggestionNote"/>
	<modified xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-11-08</modified>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">Refer to a person's short stature only when it is relevant. It is best to ask people which term they prefer to describe them.</rdf:value>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_145_en"/>
</rdf:Description>

<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/s_45">
	<rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#SuggestionNote"/>
	<modified xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2025-09-12</modified>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">It is recommended to refer to the gerographic or ethnic origin.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="fr">Il est recommandé de se référer à l'origine géographique ou ethnique.</rdf:value>
	<suggestionNoteFor xmlns="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#" rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/t_35_fr"/>
</rdf:Description>

<rdf:Description rdf:about="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/data/s_2">
	<rdf:type rdf:resource="http://data.europa.eu/c4p/ontology#SuggestionNote"/>
	<modified xmlns="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2024-12-20</modified>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="fr">Le terme peut être utilisé dans un contexte descriptif ou historique, auquel cas l'utilisation de guillemets est suggérée.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="de">Der Begriff kann in einem beschreibenden oder historischen Kontext gebraucht werden, sollte aber in Anführungszeichen gesetzt werden.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="en">The term can be used in a descriptive or historical context, in which case the use of quotation marks is suggested.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="it">Il termine può essere utilizzato in contesto storico o descrittivo, ma in tal caso è suggerito l'uso delle virgolette.</rdf:value>
	<rdf:value xml:lang="nl">De term kan gebruikt worden in een beschrijvende of historische context. Gebruik in dat geval aanhalingstekens.</rdf:value>
